title: EU urged to confront China over ‘voracious’ squid fishing
summary_full: Humboldt squid can grow up to 2.5 metres and weigh around 50 kilos. Much of the EU's squid consumption comes from Chinese vessels, accused both of rampant overfishing and exploiting crew members
